name: Moltres
Dialogue: Gyaoo!

name: Trainer 1
Dialogue: I wonder if you are good enough for me!

name: Trainer 1 after
Dialogue: I never wanted to lose to anybody!

name: Trainer 2
Dialogue: I can see you're good! Let me see exactly how good!

name: Trainer 2 after
Dialogue: I concede, you're better than me!

name: Trainer 3
Dialogue: VICTORY ROAD is the final test for trainers!

name: Trainer 3 after
Dialogue: If you get stuck, try moving some boulders around!

name: Trainer 4
Dialogue: Ah, so you wish to challenge the ELITE FOUR?

name: Trainer 4 after
Dialogue: Rival also came through here!

name: Trainer 5
Dialogue: Come on! I'll whip you!

name: Trainer 5 after
Dialogue: You earned the right to be on VICTORY ROAD!

name: Trainer 6
Dialogue: Is VICTORY ROAD too tough?

name: Trainer 6 after
Dialogue: Many trainers give up the challenge here.

name: Trainer 7
Dialogue: If you can get through here, you can go meet the ELITE FOUR!

name: Trainer 7 after
Dialogue: I can beat you when it comes to knowledge about POKEMON!

name: Trainer 8
Dialogue: I heard rumors of a child prodigy!

name: Trainer 8 after
Dialogue: You beat GIOVANNI of TEAM ROCKET?

name: Trainer 9
Dialogue: Trainers live to seek stronger opponents!

name: Trainer 9 after
Dialogue: By fighting tough battles, you get stronger!

name: Trainer 10
Dialogue: Only the chosen can pass here!

name: Trainer 10 after
Dialogue: All trainers here are headed to the POKEMON LEAGUE! Be careful!

name: Trainer 11
Dialogue: I'll show you just how good you are!

name: Trainer 11 after
Dialogue: You showed me just how good I was!
